-	Clear span warehouse with high bay storage

-	Commencing Income of $50,000 Net P.A. 
-	Leased to Granite Design for an initial 5 year term 
-	Fixed rental growth of 4% P.A. 
-	Situated on 759sqm In2 General Industry B zoned land 

Contact Exclusive Agent Jack Hardy from CBRE for further information or an inspection.
